sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Dataset
    participant A as Agent
    participant M as Model
    participant E as Environment
    participant G as Grader
    participant B as Batch Buffer

    D->>A: 1. Provide Initial Prompt (e.g., "what is the weather?")
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over A,E: Agentic Loop (Multi-turn Trajectory)
        loop Until episode complete
            A->>M: 2a. Prompt Model with current history
            M-->>A: 2b. Generate response (e.g., Tool Call intention)
            
            alt If Model wants to use a Tool
                A->>E: 2c. Execute Action/Tool Call
                E-->>A: 2d. Observation / Tool Result
            else If Model produces final answer
                Note over A: Episode ends
            end
        end
    end
    
    A->>G: 3. Submit completed trajectory
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over G,E: Grading Phase
        G->>E: 4a. Run tests / compile code in sandbox
        E-->>G: 4b. Test results (e.g., Pass/Fail)
    end
    
    G-->>A: 5. Return Reward (Positive/Negative)
    
    A->>B: 6. Store (Prompt, Trajectory, Reward)
